&lt;p&gt;Rainbow is a new ward opening at Barnet for patients with acute medical problems . We are looking for two highly motivated individuals to join the team as band 6 leaders&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The band 6 role will be integral to delivering world class care and supporting an established team settle into a new environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We value our staff and if successful we would be working with yourselves to develop not only the care of our patient but your career too&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The division has it own a credited courses and we actively develop staff skills both in clinically and leadership&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Karen Kirwilliam&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Matron&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: karenkirwilliam@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
